WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Welcome to the Yentl validation panel.

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:10.000
The city library budget increased by 12 percent this year, according to the mayor's office.

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:17.000
That number needs context because the technology grant expired.

00:00:17.000 --> 00:00:25.000
If we do not ban every social platform by Friday, schools will collapse and nobody will learn anything.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:33.000
That is a slippery slope. Which platforms create measurable distraction, and what evidence supports the claim?
